{
  "info": {
    "name": "dcm4chee-arc REST API",
    "description": "Koleksi lengkap REST API endpoint untuk dcm4chee-arc\ndcm4chee-arc: https://github.com/dcm4che/dcm4chee-arc-light\n\n## Setup\n1. Import collection ke Postman\n2. Set environment variables:\n   - `host`: IP server (default: localhost)\n   - `kc_port`: Keycloak port (default: 8843)\n   - `arc_port`: Archive port (default: 8443)\n   - `username`: Keycloak user (default: root)\n   - `password`: Keycloak password (default: changeit)\n   - `aet`: AE Title (default: DCM4CHEE)\n3. Matikan SSL verification di Postman Settings\n4. Request apapun akan auto-generate token via Pre-request Script",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "dcm4chee"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Access Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.access_token);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', jsonData.refresh_token);",
                  "console.log('Token obtained successfully');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "dcm4chee-arc-ui"
                },
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{username}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{password}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                },
                {
                  "key": "scope",
                  "value": "openid"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://{{host}}:{{kc_port}}/realms/dcm4che/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{kc_port}}",
              "path": ["realms", "dcm4che", "protocol", "openid-connect", "token"]
            },
            "description": "Dapatkan access token dari Keycloak untuk autentikasi API."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoint autentikasi Keycloak"
    },
    {
      "name": "🏥 QIDO-RS (Query)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Studies",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://{{host}}:{{arc_port}}/dcm4chee-arc/aets/{{aet}}/rs/studies?limit=10",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": ["{{host}}"],
              "port": "{{arc_port}}",
              "path": ["dcm4chee-arc", "aets", "{{aet}}", "rs", "studies"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "limit", "value": "10"},
                {"key": "offset", "value": "0", "disabled": true},
                {"key": "PatientName", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                {"key": "PatientID", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                {"key": "StudyDate", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                {"key": "Modality", "value": "", "disabled": true},
                {"key": "fuzzy", "value": "true", "disabled": true}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Query semua studies. Bisa difilter dengan parameter."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Studies - Count",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
